room_title: Escape room "Infectious Lab" by Psycho 60 Escape Rooms in Winston-Salem
room_address: 950 Graves Street, Suite H, Kernersville, NC 27284
room_description: When you return to your research lab from lunch, you immediately realize something terrible has happened. One of your test samples was left open and now the room is infected with a deadly airborne virus. The facility is on lockdown, and your only chance for survival is finding the antidote before the damage is irreversible!
